The above YAML contains 2 tables, one for capabilities and the other for the associate slots.  We need to determine if any of these are relevant to user requests.  Slots and their values can only be returned in a determination if the associated capability is a determined match for the user request.  Multiple capabilities can be selected.  If no capabilities are determined to match, then the follow response should be returned.

{
    "capabilities": [
    {
    "capability_id": "None found",
    "slots": {
        "None Found": "NULL"
      }
    }
    ]
}

A user has requested the following:

“help with 401K”

Determine which capabilities should be recommended to the user and capture any corresponding slots.  If there are examples of slot values, those examples are either actual values or similar to the values that can be returned.

The output should be in JSON as follows where examples "<>" means the actual value ("<slot_id>" = "abc123"):
{
    "capabilities": [
{
"capability_id": "<intent_id1>",
"slots": {
            "<slot1_id>": "<slot1_value>",
            "<slot2_id>": "<slot2_value>"
}
}
]
}
